{"tid":1632873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港人講地】【緊急闢謠】網傳將宣布停市停工停學 政府：有關傳聞純屬謠言","createTime":"2019-10-07T00:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T00:28:38.000Z","uid":325258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f7cc4f4f34a487d2a300409080774269f53454","tid":1632873,"uid":325258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qTFduX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTFduX0.jpg&h=8899b269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【港人講地】針對有人在社交媒體發布消息，稱行政長官即將再根據《緊急法》（即《緊急情況規例條例》），宣布星期二及三停市、停工及停學；並且凍結香港人的資產，政府發言人昨日（6日）澄清有關傳聞純屬謠言，絕非事實。發言人提醒市民要認清這些社交媒體謠傳的意圖，是製造恐慌，令香港社會陷入進一步混亂。<br />\n<br />\n發言人稱，政府考慮到目前公共安全受到廣泛危害的迫切情況，訂立《禁蒙面法》，以加強警隊執法和對意圖違法者產生阻嚇作用，遏止暴力，盡快讓香港社會回復平靜。這絕非隨意的做法，而是一個困難但必須的決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關香港金融管理局（金管局）會訂立《提款法》限制市民每日提款金額的傳言，金管局今日已經發表聲明，強調絕無此事。該局並指香港銀行體系十分穩健，銀行有充足流動資金應付市民的需要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/49417/-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E5%B8%82%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%9C%E5%AD%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E%E7%B4%94%E5%B1%AC%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F49417%2F-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2597%25A2%25E8%25AC%25A0-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%25A8%2580&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2b5a7552\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/49417/-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E5%B8%82%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%9C%E5%AD%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E%E7%B4%94%E5%B1%AC%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80</a>"},{"pid":"6ff0c36915e277ae0c62075b441f87da48ce1d4e","tid":1632873,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:26:46.000Z","msg":"今日謠言，明日法例"},{"pid":"b4ae3e6af3ec1d6919c5957acc7b6d7bcccff77a","tid":1632873,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:27:16.000Z","msg":"佢開始夠話唔會出蒙面，㩒唔㩒錢？you諗you la"},{"pid":"354fb5c2997ef7e6b08e64e440f8f27fc541e09f","tid":1632873,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"冇保證唔會喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d97b613fc1401a15518d0d8b8274cc64241aba","tid":1632873,"uid":297045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:28:38.000Z","msg":"起左底, 樓主依條友一味POST港人講地. <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲, 自己判斷"}]}